{
  "stem": "20088.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 17.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And then, of course, later it was all very easy to round up all the Jews.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "In Belgium, they didn't do that, and the Jews were much safer for a long time.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "So we had to register, and-- with address and name and everything.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then slowly they took the measures against the Jews.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We were not allowed to go out after 8 o'clock.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We were not allowed to go shopping in Christian shop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "Only in Jewish shops.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "Only between certain hours.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "We were not allowed to go in tram or have cars or have bicycles.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we as children, at first didn't think it was so bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And especially because a lot of the Christians started to wear the yellow star as well.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they went with the yellow star into the tram.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if somebody said something to them, they said, well, we are not Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We just wear that star.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But of course, that was-- the Germans didn't like that at all, and they took hostages.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they said, if this isn't going to stop, the Christian are going to wear star.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They're going to shoot the hostages.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So of course they stopped as well.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a Nazi saw that it was a Jewish boy walking with a-- perhaps Christian boy.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he ask him.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he saw he was a Jewish boy who didn't wear his star.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he said, come with me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was arrested, and the boy was never seen or heard of any more.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were not allowed to go anymore to our ordinary schools as well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My brother, Heinz, went with Margot to a Jewish school.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was quite a far walk.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
